  "dct_description_sm": [
    "New York City Commuter Rail Stations is a point theme representing New York City Transit commuter rail stations for the Long Island and Metro North rail road systems. Attribute data include the names of the stations, names of the lines, names of the railroads and type of station. Raw data was acquired from files from the New York State Department of Transportation. Data is provided in the projection NAD83 to align with the NYCMap basemap. The realigned data has not been thoroughly checked for accuracy"
  ],
